			"45": "<sup class=\"versenum\">45&#xA0;</sup>So when he found out from the centurion, he granted the body to Joseph. ",
			"46": "<sup class=\"versenum\">46&#xA0;</sup>Then he bought fine linen, took Him down, and wrapped Him in the linen. And he laid Him in a tomb which had been hewn out of the rock, and rolled a stone against the door of the tomb. ",
			"47": "<sup class=\"versenum\">47&#xA0;</sup>And Mary Magdalene and Mary <i>the mother</i> of Joses observed where He was laid."
