			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19&#xA0;</sup>So then, after the Lord had spoken to them, He was received up into heaven, and sat down at the right hand of God. ",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20&#xA0;</sup>And they went out and preached everywhere, the Lord working with <i>them</i> and confirming the word through the accompanying signs. Amen."
